#EXTM3U

# Self-hosted IPTV template for SwitchBOX development.
# Replace the example URLs below with media URLs you control.
# Recommended:
# - 1 short MP4 for fast regression checks
# - 1 higher bitrate MP4 for performance checks
# - 1 HLS .m3u8 for live/segmented playback checks
# - 1 optional audio-first stream if you want to test non-video behavior
#
# Notes:
# - Use HTTP or HTTPS URLs reachable by the Switch.
# - If you host the playlist yourself, the playlist URL can also be added
#   directly as an IPTV source in SwitchBOX.

#EXTINF:-1 group-title="Local Dev" tvg-id="local.short.mp4" tvg-name="Local Short MP4",Local Short MP4
https://example.com/media/local-short.mp4

#EXTINF:-1 group-title="Local Dev" tvg-id="local.high-bitrate.mp4" tvg-name="Local High Bitrate MP4",Local High Bitrate MP4
https://example.com/media/local-high-bitrate.mp4

#EXTINF:-1 group-title="Local Dev" tvg-id="local.hls" tvg-name="Local HLS Stream",Local HLS Stream
https://example.com/live/local-test/master.m3u8

#EXTINF:-1 group-title="Local Dev" tvg-id="local.alt" tvg-name="Local Alternate Test Stream",Local Alternate Test Stream
https://example.com/media/local-alt-test.mp4
